      "title": "Acting President Prime Minister Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena says that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has appointed Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe as Acting President.",
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena says that the President has made this appointment according to Article 37 (1) of the Constitution."
      ],
